category.name: pets/animals
description:
Does this sound familiar?

You are planning your vacation but the big question is what to do with your cat? You want it to be in good hands but you also want to give it as little stress as possible. 
How about we take care of each other's cat?

You can find more info on how our group works via http://www.kattevenner.dk

If you want to register, you have to have a user with your first and last name and you'll have to answer a few profile questions.

The group is international therefore the english language will be used.
name: Denmark Cat-Sitting Exchange
organizer.name: Jonelle
topics: [{'urlkey': 'cats', 'name': 'Cat', 'id': 121}]

category.name: pets/animals
description:
For dogs that have people but find that their human(s) can be a bit slow at times when it comes to important dog issues. This is especially true for international dogs whose human does not know where to find good places to run, meet other dogs, deal with dog/human communication, find affordable dog food, toys, snacks, vet care, etc.

This group can supply opportunities for dogs and their humans to meet in amiable surroundings and do what comes naturally: sniff butt, chase sticks, balls, play games of chase and be chased, etc., etc. (all with a good supply of snacks nearby, of course).

The group is also open to humans currently unaccompanied by a canine. If you would like to meet various dogs and their people to discuss dog care, dog adoption and any other aspect of dog life you are welcome to join us.
name: Dogenhagen: A Pet Project
organizer.name: Andrew Madsen

category.name: pets/animals
description:
Welcome all cat lovers in Skåne county! "Dogs have masters; cats have servants.” If this sounds like your house, this group is for you. If you would like to get together with other cat owners in the area to socialise, share tips, tricks and stories about life with our cute and curious cats and exchange cat sitting, let’s meet up. We hope to build community of cat lovers through regular, monthly meetings for fika and sweets. As a community we will learn how to help each other to become (as close as possible to) perfect cat owners and to ensure that our cats find good care also when they almost perfect owners are away. Everyone welcome, but residents of Skåne especially encouraged to join!

Please visit the 'page' category, there is written how to use this group web-page.

Have a good day and I am looking forward to see you.
name: Cat-Sitting Exchange in Malmö, Skåne.

If you would like to get together with other cat owners in the area to socialise, share tips, tricks and stories about life with our cute and curious cats and exchange cat sitting, let’s meet up. We hope to build community of cat lovers through regular, monthly meetings for fika and sweets. As a community we will learn how to help each other to become (as close as possible to) perfect cat owners and to ensure that our cats find good care also when they almost perfect owners are away. Everyone welcome, but residents of Skåne especially encouraged to join!

Please visit the 'page' category, there is written how to use this group web-page.

Have a good day and I am looking forward to see you.
name: Cat-Sitting Exchange in Malmö, Skåne.

description:
Does this sound familiar?

You are planning your vacation but the big question is what to do with your cat? You want it to be in good hands but you also want to give it as little stress as possible. 
How about we take care of each other's cat?

You can find more info on how our group works via http://www.kattevenner.dk

If you want to register, you have to have a user with your first and last name and you'll have to answer a few profile questions.

The group is international therefore the english language will be used.

category.name: pets/animals
description:
For dogs that have people but find that their human(s) can be a bit slow at times when it comes to important dog issues. This is especially true for international dogs whose human does not know where to find good places to run, meet other dogs, deal with dog/human communication, find affordable dog food, toys, snacks, vet care, etc.

This group can supply opportunities for dogs and their humans to meet in amiable surroundings and do what comes naturally: sniff butt, chase sticks, balls, play games of chase and be chased, etc., etc. (all with a good supply of snacks nearby, of course).

The group is also open to humans currently unaccompanied by a canine. If you would like to meet various dogs and their people to discuss dog care, dog adoption and any other aspect of dog life you are welcome to join us.
name: Dogenhagen: A Pet Project

description:
Does this sound familiar?

You are planning your vacation but the big question is what to do with your cat? You want it to be in good hands but you also want to give it as little stress as possible. 
How about we take care of each other's cat?

You can find more info on how our group works via http://www.kattevenner.dk

If you want to register, you have to have a user with your first and last name and you'll have to answer a few profile questions.

The group is international therefore the english language will be used.

category.name: pets/animals
description:
For dogs that have people but find that their human(s) can be a bit slow at times when it comes to important dog issues. This is especially true for international dogs whose human does not know where to find good places to run, meet other dogs, deal with dog/human communication, find affordable dog food, toys, snacks, vet care, etc.

This group can supply opportunities for dogs and their humans to meet in amiable surroundings and do what comes naturally: sniff butt, chase sticks, balls, play games of chase and be chased, etc., etc. (all with a good supply of snacks nearby, of course).

The group is also open to humans currently unaccompanied by a canine. If you would like to meet various dogs and their people to discuss dog care, dog adoption and any other aspect of dog life you are welcome to join us.
name: Dogenhagen: A Pet Project

category.name: pets/animals
description:
Welcome all cat lovers in Skåne county! "Dogs have masters; cats have servants.” If this sounds like your house, this group is for you. If you would like to get together with other cat owners in the area to socialise, share tips, tricks and stories about life with our cute and curious cats and exchange cat sitting, let’s meet up. We hope to build community of cat lovers through regular, monthly meetings for fika and sweets. As a community we will learn how to help each other to become (as close as possible to) perfect cat owners and to ensure that our cats find good care also when they almost perfect owners are away. Everyone welcome, but residents of Skåne especially encouraged to join!

Please visit the 'page' category, there is written how to use this group web-page.

Have a good day and I am looking forward to see you.
name: Cat-Sitting Exchange in Malmö, Skåne.
